game.name: Jetpack Master
game.description:
Jetpack Master game is a free online fun and addicting "endless running" adventure game for kids. In order to survive in this platform game, all you need to do is walk for as long distance as you can. Use you ultra-cool aerophone jetpack to beat all the hindrances that you will come to your side-scrolling obstacle course. Get yourself ready to face different obstacles like laser beams, dangerous robots as well as other futuristic hindrances in this exclusively-designed flash game.

In Jetpack Master game you will get a chance to play the role of Jeff Powers, who is a very powerful superhero. So, roll up your sleeves to set out on a journey filled with many unexpected challenges. In this cool flash game, your mission is to reach out to a deserted space station. Be focused on accomplishing the quests and avoiding obstacles, rockets as well as evil robots. Don?t forget to collect the maximum possible coins, tokens and burgers to ensure the victory in this highly challenging game. You can use them to upgrade your hero! Are you ready to get the high score?

This awesome adventure game features excellent graphics and easy-to-use interface. Help Jeff Powers to go through an abandoned space station, evade the incoming danger and reach the final destination. In order to upgrade your hero, new equipment, special power-ups, use the tokens, burgers and coins you have collected during your journey. This latest platform game requires sharp observation skills, fun action, stamina and determination, as well as good hand-eye coordination. Complete your missions, collect as much as gold coins as you can and beat your previous high score! Good luck!
